Dua for Cure from Illness

الَّلهُمَّ لاَ تُشَمِت أعَدائي بِدائي، واجعل القرآن العَظيم شِفائي ودَوائي أنتَ ثقتي ورَجائي واجعل حُسنَ ظني بِكَ شِفائي

allahuma la tashmit ‘aedayiy bidayiy, wajeal alquran aleazim shifayiy wadawayiy ‘ant thiqati warajayiy wajeal husn zaniy bik shifayiy

Oh God, do not gloat over my enemies, my primitiveness, and make the great Quran my cure and my medicine, you are my trust and my hope, and make my good faith in you my cure.

Dua for Protection from Loneliness & Isolation

الَّلهُمَّ إنِي أعَوُذْ بِكَ من عُقْوق الأبنَاء، ومن قَطيِعةّ الأقرباء، ومن جَفوْة الأحَيِاء، ومن تَغيِر الأصدقاَء.

allahuma ‘iiniy ‘aeudh bik min euquq al’abna’i, wamin qatieat al’aqriba’i, wamin jafwat al’ahya’i, waman taghayur al’asdiqa’i.

O Allah, I seek refuge in You from the disobedience of children, from the estrangement of relatives, from the harshness of the living, and from the loss of friends.

The Master Dua

الَّلهُمَّ أَفتَح لَنَا أَبْوَاب رحَمتِك ورِزقك ونَسألُكَ الشِفاء لِمن مَسّهُ الضُر والرحمةٍ لِمن ضَمَهُ اَلقَبر والفَرجّ لِمن ضَاق به الصدر، وإجعَلنا يا الله مِمَن عَفوتَ ورَضيتَ عَنهُم وغَفَرتَ لَهُم وحَرمتَهُم عَلى النَار وكَتَبتَ لهُم اَلجنّة وإرزُقَنا الأمنَ والأمَان والسَلامةً والإسلاَم واَلعَوْنَ عَلىَ اَلصَلاةَ واَلصِيام والقِيام وتِلاوة القُرأَن

‏allalhuma ‘aftah lana ‘abwab rhamtk waruzqik wnasaluk alshifa’ limn massh aldur walrhmt limn dmah alqabr walfarj limn daq bih alsadri, w’ijealna ya allah miman eafwt wradyt eanhum wghafart lahum wharmtahum eala alnar wkatabt lhum aaljnnt w’irzuqana alamn walaman walsalamtan wal’islaam waaleawn eala aalsalat waalsiam walqiam wtilawt alqur’an

O Allah, open the doors of Your mercy and sustenance for us. We ask You for healing for those who have been afflicted by harm, mercy for those who are afflicted by the grave, and relief for those who are facing difficulties. Make us, O Allah, from the ones who are released from the hellfire, whom You are pleased with, and whom you have forgiven, and forbid them from the fire and write for them the Paradise. Grant us security, safety, peace, and Islam. And assist us in prayers, fasting, the late night prayers, and in reciting the Quran.

الَّلهُمَّ ثَبت عَلي عَقلي ودِيني وبِكَ ياَرب ثَبت لي يِقيِني وأرزُقني رِزقاً حَلاَلاً يِكفِيني وأبعد عَني شَر من يؤذِيني ولا تَحوْجني لِطبيب يِدَاوْيني

allalhumm thabt ealy eaqly wdiny wbik yaarb thabt li yiqyiny warzuqny rizqaan halaalaan yikfiny wa’ubeid eany shar man ywdhiny wala tahwjny litbyb yidawyny

Oh God, make my mind and my religion firm on me, and through You, O Lord, make my certainty firm for me, and grant me a lawful provision that suffices me, and keep away from me the evil of those who harm me, and do not make me in need of a doctor to heal me.

Dua to Ease Your Life From Anxiety

اللَّهُمَّ فَرّج أُموراً ضَاقت بها صُدورنا وعَجزت بها حِيلتنا وقلّ بها صَبرنا ، الّلهمّ أَسعِد قلوبنا بما أنتَ أعْلَمُ بِهِ مِنّا ، اللّهُمّ اجِعَل مانُريدُه في حياتِنا قريباً لِناظِرنَا سَعيداً لخواطِرنَا ، اللّهِمّ أسْعدنَا سعادتين الدّنْيا بِخيرِها والجنّةِ بِفردَوسها .

lllhm frrj ‘umwraan daqt biha sudwrna waeajazt biha hilatana wql biha sabrna , alllhm ‘aseid qulubina bima ant aelam bih minna , alllhm ajeal manuryduh fi hyatina qrybaan linazirna saeydaan lkhwatirna , alllhm asedna saeadatayn alddnya bikhyriha waljnnt bifrdawsha

Oh Allah, ease the matters that are heavy on our chests, for which we have no solution, and no more patience. O Allah, make our hearts happy with what You know, but we are not aware. O Allah, make what we need in our lives close to our vision and happiness for our thoughts. O Allah, give us two happinesses: in life with the good in it, and in Paradise with the highest ranking.

Dua for Power & Respect

الَّلهُمَّ ياَ قَوْي ياَ جَّباَر، أَرفَع شَأني وكَلِلني بالقوة والهَيبة ما حَييت، ولا تَزرع الغُرْور بقَلبي، إنَكَ على كل شيء قَدِير وبالإجَابِة جَدِير.

allahuma ya qawi ya jabari, arfae shani wakulalani bialquat walhaybat ma hayitu, wala tazrae alghurur biqalbi, ‘iinak ealaa kuli shay’ qadir wabial’iijabat jadiar.

Oh Allah, O Powerful, O Mighty, raise my status and entrust me with strength and prestige as long as I live, and do not sow arrogance in my heart, for You are capable of everything and competent 
of answering.

Dua to Pay Your Debts & Protect from Poverty

لا إِلَهَ إِلا اللَّهُ الْحَلِيمُ الْكَرِيمُ سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَرْشِ الْعَظِيمِ الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ مُوجِبَاتِ رَحْمَتِكَ وَعَزَائِمَ مَغْفِرَتِكَ وَالْغَنِيمَةَ مِنْ كُلِّ بِرٍّ وَالسَّلامَةَ مِنْ كُلِّ إِثْمٍ أَسْأَلُكَ أَلا تَدَعَ لِي ذَنْبًا إِلا غَفَرْتَهُ وَلا هَمًّا إِلا فَرَّجْتَهُ وَلا حَاجَةً هِيَ لَكَ رِضًا إِلا قَضَيْتَهَا اقْضِ عنّا الديْنَ وأغنِنا من الفقرِ

La ilaha illallah Al-Halimul-Karim. Subhan Allah Rabbil-`Arshil-`Azim. Al-Hamdulillahi Rabbil-`Alamin. As’aluka mujibati rahmatika wa `aza’im maghfiratika, wal-ghanimata min kulli birrin, was-salamata min kulli ithmin, la tada` li dhanban illa ghafartahu, wa la hamman illa farrajtahu, wa la Hajatan hiya laka ridan Illa Qadaitaha, ya arham ar-rahimin aqd enna aldyn waghnina min alfqr

None has the right to be worshiped but Allah. Al-Halim (the Forbearing) Al-Karim (the Generous). Glorious is Allah, Lord of the Magnificent Throne. All praise is due to Allah, Lord of the worlds. I ask You for that which warrants Your mercy, and that which will determine Your forgiveness, and the spoils (fruits) of every righteous deed, and safety from every sin; do not leave a sin for me without forgiving it, nor a worry without relieving it. Or a need that pleases you without granting it. O Most-Merciful of those who have mercy:  Pay our debt and enrich us from poverty.

(Dua for when you are in need)

Dua for Cure from Disease 

بسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ أَعُوذُ بِعِزَّةِ اللَّهِ وَ قُدْرَتِهِ عَلَى الْأَشْيَاءِ أُعِيذُ نَفْسِي بِجَبَّارِ السَّمَاءِ أُعِيذُ نَفْسِي بِمَنْ لَا يَضُرُّ مَعَ اسْمِهِ دَاءٌ أُعِيذُ نَفْسِي بِالَّذِي اسْمُهُ دَوَاءٌ أُعِيذُ نَفْسِي بِالَّذِي اسْمُهُ بَرَكَةٌ وَ شِفَاءٌ.

In the Name of Allah, the Merciful, the Compassionate: O Allah, I ask You by Your Pure, Immaculate, Most Holy and Blessed Name, by Which whoever asks of You, You grant him, and by Which whoever calls on You, You answer him.
I take refuge in the Might of Allah-Power over things. I seek protection for myself in the Omnipotent of the Heavens. I seek protection for myself in the One with Whose Name no disease harms. I seek refuge for myself in the One Whose Name is a Blessing and a Cure.

Dua to Heal Any Illness

بِسْمِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ بِاسْمِكَ الطَّاهِرِ الْمُطَهَّرِ الْقُدُّوسِ الْمُبَارَكِ الَّذِي مَنْ سَأَلَكَ بِهِ أَعْطَيْتَهُ وَ مَنْ دَعَاكَ بِهِ أَجَبْتَهُ أَنْ تُصَلِّيَ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَ آلِهِ وَ أَنْ تُعَافِيَنِي مِمَّا أَجِدُ فِي رَأْسِي وَ فِي سَمْعِي وَ فِي بَصَرِي وَ فِي بَطْنِي وَ فِي ظَهْرِي وَ فِي يَدَيَّ وَ فِي رِجْلَيَّ وَ فِي جَسَدِي وَ فِي جَمِيعِ أَعْضَائِي وَ جَوَارِحِي إِنَّكَ لَطِيفٌ لِمَا تَشَاءُ وَ أَنْتَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْ‏ءٍ قَدِيرٌ.

bism alrrahman alrrahim alllahumm ‘inni ‘as’aluk biasmik alttahir almutahhar alquddus almubarak alladhi man sa’alak bih ‘aetaytah w man daeak bih ‘ajabtah ‘an tusalli ealaa muhammad w alih w ‘an tueafiani mimma ‘ajid fi rasi w fi samei w fi basari w fi batni w fi zahri w fi yaday w fi rijlay w fi jasadi w fi jamie ‘aedayiy w jawarihi ‘innak latif lima tasha’ w ‘ant ealaa kull shay‏’ qadir

In the name of Allah  the Merciful, the Compassionate: O Allah I plead to Your Pure, Immaculate, Most Holy and Blessed Name, by which whoever asks of You, You Grant him, and by which whoever calls on You, You answer him, to bless Mohammed (saws) and his family, and to heal the suffering in my head, my hearing, my sight, my belly, my back, my hand, my foot, my body, and in my all my organs and limbs. Surely, You are gracious to whomsoever You will, and You are powerful over all things.

اللهم أبطل كل سحر إن كان مأكول أو مشروب، باسمك اللهم أبطل كل سحر معقود أو مرشوش

Dua for a Righteous Spouse

اللهمّ يا جامع النّاس ليومٍ لا ريب فيه اجمعني مع من تحب وترضى في الدّنيا والآخرة، يا من أمره بين الكاف والنون، ويقول للشيء كن فيكون، ارزقني بزوجٍ صالح وذريّة صالحة تقرّ بها عيني وعين أبي وأمّي يا ودود يا ودود  يا ذا العرش المجيد يا فعّال لما تريد.

allhm ya jamie alnnas lywm la rayb fih ajmaeni mae man tuhibu watardaa fi alddnya walakhirati, ya min ‘amrih bayn alkaf walnuwna, wayaqul lilshay’ kun fayakun, arzuqni bzwj salih wdhryt salihat tqr biha eayniun waeayin ‘abi wammy ya wadud ya wadud ya dha alearsh almajid ya feeal lima turidu.

Oh Allah, You are the one who gathers people for a day when there is no doubt, gather me with whomever You love and are satisfied with in this world and the hereafter. All matters are in Your hands. If you say “Be” it will be. 
Grant me a righteous [wife or husband] and a righteous offspring to please my vision, and the vision of my father and mother, O Most-Loving, O Most-Loving, O Owner of the Glorious Throne, You are the one who does what You want.

Dua for Happiness & Peace of Mind

الَّلهُمَّ مَن أعَتزّ بِكَ فَلَن يُذَل، ومن إهَتدى بِكَ فَلن يِضِلّ، ومن إستَكثر بك فَلن يِقلّ، ومن إستَقوى بِكَ فَلن يضعَف، ومن إستَغنى بِكَ فَلَن يِفتَقر، ومن إستَنصر بِكَ فلن يُخذل، ومن إستَعان بك فلن يُغلب، ومن تَوكل عليكَ فَلن يِخيب. الَّلهُمَّ كُن لَنا وُليا ونَصيرا ومعينَا ومُجيرا إنك كُنتَ بِنا بَصيرا.

alullahum man aeatz bik falan yudhal, waman ‘ihatda bik faln ydill, waman ‘istakthr bik faln yqll, waman ‘istaqwa bik faln ydeaf, waman ‘iistaghnaa bik falan yiftaqr, waman aistansar bik falan yukhdhl, waman ‘istaean bik falan yughlb, waman tawakal elyk falan yakhibi 
allahuma kun lana waliana wanasiran wamueaynan wamujiran ‘iinak kunt bina basiran

O Allah, he who cherishes You will not be humiliated, he who is guided by You will not go astray, he who seeks help from You will not diminish, he who seeks strength in You will not be weak, he who seeks help from You will not be destitute, he who seeks help from You will not be defeated, he who trusts in You will not be disappointed. Oh Allah, be our guardian, supporter, helper and protector. You are a visionary of us.

Dua to Guide & Protect Your Children

 
الَّلهُمَّ يِامُغَيّر الحَال والأحَوُال،
غَيرّ حَالِ أولاَدي إليَ أحسَنِ حَال.
الَّلهُمَّ إني أعَيزُهُمَ مِن هَمً يِرُهَقْهُم وبُكَاءٍ 
يِحزنَهُم وكَربً يِفُجِعَهُم. 
أسَألُكَ يِاكَرِيم أن تَشرَح صُدُورَهُم،
وتَجبُر خَواطرَهُم. الَّلهُمَّ بَاعد بَينَهُم وبَينَ الفَتن مَا ظَهرَ مِنهَا ومَا بَطن . الَّلهُمَّ إجَعَلهُم منَ الصَالِحيِن ولِكِتَابِك َحَافِظِين.
الَّلهُمَّ ًإرزُقَهُم حُبَك وحُبِ مَن يِحَبَك .

allalhumm yiamughayr alhal walahawual,
ghayr hal awlaady ‘ily ahsan hal.
allalhumm ‘iiniy aeayzuhum min haman yiruhaqhum wbuka’
yihznahum wkarban yifujieahum.
asaluk yiakarim ‘an tashrah sudurahum,
wtajbur khawatrahum. allalhumm baed baynahum wbayn alfatn ma zahr minha wma batn . allalhumm ‘ijaealhum mn alsalihyin wlikitabik ahafizin.
allalhumm ً’irzuqahum hubak whub man yihabak

Oh Allah, Changer of conditions and status,
Change the condition of my children for the better.
Oh Allah, protect them from sadness that makes them tired,  crying that makes them sad, and calamity that shocks them.
I ask you, O Generous One, to bring happiness to their hearts and comfort them.
Oh Allah, keep them away from temptations, whether apparent or hidden. 
Oh Allah, make them among the righteous, and those who are guided by Your Book.
Oh Allah, grant them your love and the love of those who love you.

الَّلهُمَّ أعِزَّنَا بِعِزَّكَ وَقُوَّتِكَ ،وأنْصُرْنَا بِنَصْرِكَ وَسُلطَانِكَ، وأدْفَعْ عَنَّا شَرَّ الْأشْرَارِ ،وَكَيْدَ الْكَهَنَهِ والسَّحَرهِ والْفُجَّارِ ،والْمَرض فِي اللَّيْلِ والنَّهاَر.

allalhumm aeizzana bieizzak waquwwatik ,wansurna binasrik wasultanika, wadfae eanna sharr alashrar ,wakayd alkahanah walssaharh walfujjar ,walmard fi alllayl walnnahaar.
